</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-thumbnail"><div class="field-content imageleft"> <a href="/blog/news-and-events/world-literature-today-co-host-online-resistir-latin-america-poetry-event" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/blog_thumbnail/public/LatinAmerican-Resistir-anchor-graphic_0.jpg?itok=szJs6OU0" width="100" height="75" alt="An image of a fountain pen resting on scribbles in black and red. Text reads: Resistir Latin America. Online Reading Event" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-blog-thumbnail" />
</a>
</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><h4 class="field-content"><a href="https://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/news-and-events/world-literature-today-co-host-online-resistir-latin-america-poetry-event"><em>World Literature Today</em> to Co-host Online “RESISTIR Latin America” Poetry Event
</a>
</h4></div><div><div class="blog-summary">On Saturday, November 18 at 10am cst, the “RESISTIR Groupe” of<em> </em>Latin American PEN Centers, <em>World Literature Today</em>, and <em>Latin…</em>
</div></div><span class="views-field views-field-field-date"><span class="field-content date-display-single">October 31, 2023
</span></span>|<span><span class="field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/editors-wlt" hreflang="en">The Editors of WLT</a>
</span></span></div>
